Title: Addition of mk_inventory sections via node collector
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: node-collector
Date: 1652422629
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0-alpha.1

Node hosts in a Checkmk site now have the HW/SW inventory entries of a
Linux system (in addition to the standard Kubernetes entries).
Specifically, the following sections have been added:
<ul>
<li>lnx_cpuinfo</li>
<li>lnx_uname</li>
<li>lnx_video</li>
<li>lnx_block_devices</li>
</ul>
